{"tid":123571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"48歲消防隊目打排球暈倒　送院不治","createTime":"2017-02-17T02:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T06:31:46.000Z","uid":319,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c8d6683c895a004efd448e4349c59e383370c13","tid":123571,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:58:28.000Z","msg":"深井消防局昨晚7時許，一名48歲姓陳消防隊目與同僚打排球操練體能時不適暈倒，同事見狀立即為他急救，並將他送往仁濟醫院，經搶救後證實不治。警方調查後相信案件無可疑。《明報》正向消防處查詢事主是否曾遭排球打中或其他原因暈倒斃命。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170217/s00001/1487297175251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170217%2Fs00001%2F1487297175251&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8cb10121\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170217%2Fs00001%2F1487297175251&h=b6d1e785\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170217/s00001/1487297175251</a>"},{"pid":"32caed2394ffb6b22d8f95f2ca371fbc92c1a7f1","tid":123571,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907c271e73bf48a0985209822644be4208bcafa5","tid":123571,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:09:21.000Z","msg":"隱形心髒病"},{"pid":"ca44c8983779b4a87a8f158c50d6062afa60b0fa","tid":123571,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隱形心髒病</blockquote><br />\n心髒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7545f914c3f166b33141658c2dee5f179cdeda24","tid":123571,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隱形心髒病</blockquote><br />\n心髒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"